Find or create your `openclaw.json` file (usually `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json` on Linux/Mac).

Add this minimal config:

```json
{
  "messages": {
    "tts": {
      "auto": "always",
      "provider": "elevenlabs",
      "elevenlabs": {
        "apiKey": "your_elevenlabs_api_key_here",
        "voiceId": "your_voice_id_here"
      }
    }
  }
